<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8309390>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–2. Photo records of Phryganogryllacris unicolor Liu & Wang. 1 one male and one female from Wucenglazi, Helan, Liaoyang, Liaoning, China, photo by Huo Qing-Bo, 2 one female from Heigou, Dandong, Liaoning, China, photo by Liu Xing-Yue." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8309390/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8309392>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3–9. Specimens of Phryganogryllacris unicolor Liu & Wang from Fenglingu, Guanmengshan, Benxi, Liaoning, China. 3 photo by He Zhu-Qing when alive, 4 face in front view, 5 left forewing, 6 stridulatory pegs on left side, 7 dorsal view of abdominal apex, 8 ventral view of abdominal apex, 9 right hind tibia and tarsomeres." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8309392/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

